00:15:03,052 --> 00:15:03,773
Architecture?

288
00:15:04,412 --> 00:15:05,052
What?

289
00:15:05,573 --> 00:15:06,653
Can't girls study it?

290
00:15:07,492 --> 00:15:08,212
Not what I meant.

291
00:15:09,653 --> 00:15:11,693
