294
00:15:16,773 --> 00:15:18,013
Alright, I misunderstood you.

295
00:15:18,613 --> 00:15:19,332
Actually,

296
00:15:19,813 --> 00:15:21,613
my friends and relatives

297
00:15:21,693 --> 00:15:23,292
