in the city.

311
00:15:56,452 --> 00:15:57,172
Do you know it?

312
00:15:57,813 --> 00:15:58,492
I heard it is

313
00:15:58,492 --> 00:15:59,653
a female architect's work.

314
00:16:00,853 --> 00:16:01,973
You know that too?

315
00:16:03,332 --> 00:16:04,893
