00:20:26,492 --> 00:20:27,693
I must get two bags for you.

401
00:20:28,052 --> 00:20:28,773
Okay.

402
00:20:30,492 --> 00:20:31,132
Wait a moment.

403
00:20:35,933 --> 00:20:36,492
Xu Zhi,

404
00:20:36,773 --> 00:20:37,853
