420
00:21:04,292 --> 00:21:05,212
Cut the nonsense.

421
00:21:05,813 --> 00:21:07,092
Listen to me. Right now, you...

422
00:21:07,092 --> 00:21:07,893
Cai Binhong,

423
00:21:08,332 --> 00:21:09,773
