453
00:22:40,533 --> 00:22:41,292
Why today?

454
00:22:41,613 --> 00:22:42,498
None of your business.

455
00:22:44,573 --> 00:22:45,613
By the way,

456
00:22:46,893 --> 00:22:48,452
