477
00:23:33,172 --> 00:23:33,720
Got it?

478
00:23:34,212 --> 00:23:35,613
Alright, fine.

479
00:23:35,933 --> 00:23:36,853
I was wrong, alright?

480
00:23:37,452 --> 00:23:38,212
I'll stop joking.

481
00:23:43,533 --> 00:23:44,693
