557
00:27:31,212 --> 00:27:32,252
Go work in space then.

558
00:27:32,252 --> 00:27:33,013
Exactly.

559
00:27:33,853 --> 00:27:35,092
Another wave of meteors.

560
00:27:35,573 --> 00:27:37,372
Look, there are so many.

